== AGENT
Symrise, IBM

== GOAL
Determining formulas for products

== DATA
The existing fragrance formulas and compares the ingredients to customer data, such as geography, customer age and preferences.

== METHODS
Philyra machine learning algorithm, Classification, Supervied

== RESULTS
Some new formulas

== ISSUES

== SCORE
5

== COMMENTS
It is very practical, can solve a large amount of material cost and time, and shorten the sales cycle of new products, and has high commercial value. More interesting.